title: Using HTTP/2 with PHP 7 on Mac
description: On his personal blog, Rob Allen telling how to use HTTP/2 (or HTTP2.0) with PHP 7 on Mac OX X. HTTP/2 (originally named HTTP/2.0) is a major revision of the HTTP network protocol used by the World Wide Web. To know more about HTTP/2, please check https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTP/2 or https://http2.github.io
